    				Till Divorce do us Apart    			


Just a few years ago at many NRI standard weekend dinner get-to-gathers, I used to hear my friends proudly tell that marriages in India are stable, unlike these unstable western marriages.  Today I read this article in Times of India about the Mantra 2006:  Till Divorce do us Apart.  Interesting reading.



By Ramesh |
